                "text": "A patch of gluttongrass attacks with three fronds\u2014these are primary natural attacks that deals slashing damage. When gluttongrass damages a creature that can be affected by its bleed attack, the gluttongrass has 1 hit point restored. If a creature is already suffering from a bleed effect, the gluttongrass instead has 2 hit points restored for each successful frond attack. "
